'''玛丽·利娅·特朗普'''（{{lang-en|Mary Lea Trump}}，{{bd|1965年|5月3日||}}）<ref>{{Cite web|title=What to Know About Donald Trump's Niece Mary, Who Fought Him in Court & Is Writing a Tell-All|url=https://people.com/politics/what-to-know-about-donald-trump-niece-mary-trump/|accessdate=July 4, 2020|author=Carlson|date=June 15, 2020|first=Adam|work=People|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200704013654/https://people.com/politics/what-to-know-about-donald-trump-niece-mary-trump/|archivedate=July 4, 2020}}</ref>是一名[[美国|美国]]心理学家和作家。她是第45任[[美国总统|美国总统]][[唐納·川普|唐纳德·特朗普]]的侄女，曾批評他以及{{link-en|特朗普家族|Trump family}}的其他成員。她在2020年出版了一本关于他和家族的書籍《[[永不满足：我的家族如何制造出了世界上最危险的人|永不满足：我的家族如何制造出了世界上最危险的人]]》，在出版當天就賣出了近百萬本。

== 早年與生涯 ==
玛丽·特朗普出生於1965年5月，她的母親是[[空中服務員|空中服務員]]Linda Lee Clapp，父亲是[[環球航空|環球航空]]的飛行員[[小弗雷德·特朗普|小弗雷德·特朗普]]。她有一名哥哥弗雷德·特朗普三世（Frederick Trump III）。小弗雷德與其父[[弗雷德·特朗普|弗雷德·特朗普]]以及弟弟唐纳德·特朗普關係不睦，對家族產業也不感興趣，從而在[[环球航空|环球航空]]擔任一名飞行员<ref name=rfi>{{cite news |title=侄女新书爆料：特朗普高考时找枪手替考 自恋不足以形容 |url=https://www.rfi.fr/cn/%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB/20200708-%E4%BE%84%E5%A5%B3%E6%96%B0%E4%B9%A6%E7%88%86%E6%96%99-%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E9%AB%98%E8%80%83%E6%97%B6%E6%89%BE%E6%9E%AA%E6%89%8B%E6%9B%BF%E8%80%83-%E8%87%AA%E6%81%8B%E4%B8%8D%E8%B6%B3%E4%BB%A5%E5%BD%A2%E5%AE%B9 |publisher=rfi |accessdate=2020-07-11 |archive-date=2020-07-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200710160149/https://www.rfi.fr/cn/%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB/20200708-%E4%BE%84%E5%A5%B3%E6%96%B0%E4%B9%A6%E7%88%86%E6%96%99-%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E9%AB%98%E8%80%83%E6%97%B6%E6%89%BE%E6%9E%AA%E6%89%8B%E6%9B%BF%E8%80%83-%E8%87%AA%E6%81%8B%E4%B8%8D%E8%B6%B3%E4%BB%A5%E5%BD%A2%E5%AE%B9 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

1983年，瑪麗毕业于{{link-en|埃塞尔·沃克学校|Ethel Walker School}}。她後來在[[塔夫茨大學|塔夫茨大学]]學習[[英語文學|英语文学]]，並在[[哥伦比亚大学|哥伦比亚大学]]獲得英语文学硕士学位，研究課題是美國作家[[威廉·福克納|威廉·福克纳]]。<ref name="WaPo2020-07-02" /><ref name="Cnn2020-06-17">{{Cite news|author=D'Antonio|first=Michael|date=June 17, 2020|title=The psychologist in the Trump family speaks|url=https://www.cnn.com/2020/06/17/opinions/mary-trump-book-opinion-dantonio/index.html|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200702191715/https://www.cnn.com/2020/06/17/opinions/mary-trump-book-opinion-dantonio/index.html|archivedate=July 2, 2020|accessdate=|publisher=CNN}}</ref><ref>{{Cite thesis|last=Trump|first=Mary|language=en}}</ref><ref name="simonandschuster">{{Cite web|title=About the Book 'Too Much and Never Enough'|url=https://www.simonandschuster.com/books/Too-Much-and-Never-Enough/Mary-L-Trump/9781982141462|accessdate=|author=Trump|first=Mary|publisher=Simon and Schuster|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200703211027/https://www.simonandschuster.com/books/Too-Much-and-Never-Enough/Mary-L-Trump/9781982141462|archivedate=July 3, 2020}}</ref>2010年，她在{{en-link|艾德菲大學|Adelphi University}}获得[[臨床心理學|临床心理学]]博士学位。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/07/07/nyregion/mary-trump-book.html|title=The Inside Story of Why Mary Trump Wrote a Tell-All Memoir|first=Alan|author=Feuer|first2=Michael|author2=Rothfeld|first3=Maggie|last3=Haberman|work=The New York Times|date=July 7, 2020|accessdate=2020-07-11|archive-date=2020-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200708003458/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/07/07/nyregion/mary-trump-book.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> <ref>{{Cite news|url=https://chicago.suntimes.com/2020/7/7/21316205/mary-trump-book-donald-too-much-never-enough|title=Mary Trump says uncle Donald may have 'undiagnosed learning disability' in new book|first=Lynn|author=Sweet|date=July 7, 2020|work=Chicago Sun-Times|accessdate=2020-07-11|archive-date=2020-07-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200707184751/https://chicago.suntimes.com/2020/7/7/21316205/mary-trump-book-donald-too-much-never-enough|dead-url=no}}</ref>

玛丽的祖父[[弗雷德·特朗普|弗雷德·特朗普]]於1999年死于[[阿茲海默症|阿茲海默症]]後，玛丽對遺產分配不滿，認為自己與兄長的遺產份額被剝奪<ref>{{cite news |title=遗产之争、内讧与背叛：特朗普侄女为何写书爆料 |url=https://cn.nytimes.com/usa/20200709/mary-trump-book/ |publisher=紐約時報 |accessdate=2020-07-11 |archive-date=2020-07-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200712000215/https://cn.nytimes.com/usa/20200709/mary-trump-book/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，於是与[[當勞·特朗普|當勞·特朗普]]进行激烈的财产斗争<ref name=rfi/>。

2002年，[[哥倫比亞大學出版社|哥伦比亚大学出版社]]出版了瑪麗的作品《诊断：精神分裂症》（''Diagnosis: Schizophrenia''）。<ref>{{Cite book|last=Miller|first=Rachel|title=Diagnosis Schizophrenia : a comprehensive resource for patients, families, and helping professionals|url=https://archive.org/details/diagnosisschizop00mill|date=2002|publisher=Columbia University Press|others=Mason, Susan Elizabeth|isbn=0-231-50105-6|location=New York|pages=|oclc=51615777}}</ref> 她曾教授过有關心理学的研究生课程。<ref name="simonandschuster" /> 她是[[教练|生活教练]]公司The Trump Coaching Group的创始人兼首席执行官，并且他在[[美國東北部|美國東北部]]还经营着许多小型企业。<ref name="meaww">{{Cite web|title=Meet Mary Trump, the president's niece and Hillary Clinton supporter who's writing a tell-all book about POTUS|url=https://meaww.com/mary-trump-presidents-niece-hillary-clinton-supporter-trump-2016-win-worst-night-life-tell-all-book|accessdate=July 3, 2020|author=Paul|date=June 15, 2020|first=Pritha|work=meaww.com|language=en|archive-date=2020-09-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200919025119/https://meaww.com/mary-trump-presidents-niece-hillary-clinton-supporter-trump-2016-win-worst-night-life-tell-all-book|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 個人生活 ==
玛丽在16歲時，她的父親小弗雷德·特朗普於1981年9月29日死于因[[酗酒|酗酒]]引起的[[心肌梗死|心脏病]]，享年42歲。<ref name="WaPo2020-07-02">{{Cite news|work=|author=Kranish|first=Michael|date=July 2, 2020|title=Mary Trump once stood up to her uncle Donald. Now her book describes a 'nightmare' of family dysfunction.|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/mary-trump-once-stood-up-to-her-uncle-donald-now-her-book-describes-a-nightmare-of-family-dysfunction/2020/06/25/be52d7f2-b4ba-11ea-9b0f-c797548c1154_story.html|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200704023206/https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/mary-trump-once-stood-up-to-her-uncle-donald-now-her-book-describes-a-nightmare-of-family-dysfunction/2020/06/25/be52d7f2-b4ba-11ea-9b0f-c797548c1154_story.html|archivedate=July 4, 2020|accessdate=}}</ref>

瑪麗是一名女同性戀者。在《永不滿足：我的家族如何製造出了世界上最危險的人》一書中，她說她整個家族對[[同性戀恐懼|同性戀恐懼]]和偏執，使她多年來一直不敢公開同性戀，因為擔心會被斷絕關係和剝奪繼承權。瑪麗講述了她的祖母[[瑪麗·安妮·麥克勞德·特朗普|瑪麗·安妮·麥克勞德·特朗普]]經常把[[艾爾頓·約翰|艾爾頓·約翰]]稱為「{{link-en|男同性變態|Faggot (slang)}}」，瑪麗決定不[[出櫃|出櫃]]，也不告訴她和整個特朗普直系親屬。她曾經和一名女子结婚，并養育一个女儿。她後來离婚，并与女儿Avary一起住在[[紐約州|紐約州]]的[[長島|長島]]<ref name="simonandschuster" />，而她的女兒Avary是透過與精子捐贈者的體外受精懷上的。<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2020/jun/21/donald-trump-mary-lea-trump-book-memoir |title = Family business: Trump fears latest damning memoir – this time by his liberal niece |author = David Smith |date = 2020-06-21 |publisher = The Guardian |language = en |access-date = 2021-10-31 |archive-date = 2020-06-21 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200621100251/https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2020/jun/21/donald-trump-mary-lea-trump-book-memoir |dead-url = no }}</ref>

在[[2016年美國總統選舉|2016年美國总统大选]]時，她支持[[希拉里·克林顿|希拉里·克林顿]]<ref name="meaww" />。

